title: Inside Dior’s Couture Show and After-Party With Soko
text: Vogue may earn compensation on these sales through affiliate programs. See more photos of: Expand We Should All Be Feminists! Maria made such a strong and impactful statement with this T-shirt last season. I’m really happy that such a badass woman is now the creative mind behind Dior—inspiring for all of us humans out there who are fighting for equality with love and compassion and art. A great motto to live by, especially in a time like now when everyone’s freedom and differences are being shamed and compromised. I’m with her, all the way! Go, Maria! Photo: Courtesy of Soko / @sokothecat See more photos of: Expand The set looked like Alice in Wonderland in the Garden of Eden. I kind of want to build a tree house on top of this magical wish tree and move right in.
